<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Relationship Contract 💍</title>

<style>
  body{
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffdde1, #ee9ca7);
    margin:0;
    padding:20px;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
  }

  .container{
    background:white;
    width:100%;
    max-width:600px;
    padding:25px;
    border-radius:20px;
    box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  }

  h1{
    text-align:center;
    color:#ff4d6d;
  }

  label{
    font-weight:bold;
    display:block;
    margin-top:10px;
  }

  input{
    width:100%;
    padding:8px;
    margin-top:5px;
    border-radius:8px;
    border:1px solid #ccc;
  }

  .section{
    margin-top:20px;
  }

  .result{
    display:none;
    margin-top:20px;
    text-align:center;
    font-weight:bold;
    color:#ff4d6d;
  }

  button{
    width:100%;
    padding:12px;
    margin-top:20px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:10px;
    background:#ff4d6d;
    color:white;
    font-size:16px;
    cursor:pointer;
  }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<h1>💍 Relationship Contract 💍</h1>

<label>First Name:</label>
<input type="text">

<label>Middle Name:</label>
<input type="text">

<label>Last Name:</label>
<input type="text">

<label>Age:</label>
<input type="number">

<label>Birthday:</label>
<input type="date">

<label>Gmail:</label>
<input type="email">

<label>Contact Number:</label>
<input type="text">

<label>Date Today:</label>
<input type="date">

<div class="section">
<input type="checkbox"> Terms and Conditions Agreed
</div>

<hr>

<h3>📜 PROMISE SECTION 📜</h3>

<p>Do you promise to be my partner in life?</p>
<input type="radio" name="q1"> Yes<br>
<input type="radio" name="q1"> Of course<br>
<input type="radio" name="q1"> Why not?<br>

<p>Will you take care of me for the rest of my life?</p>
<input type="radio" name="q2"> Yes<br>
<input type="radio" name="q2"> Of course<br>
<input type="radio" name="q2"> Always<br>

<p>Do you promise not to hurt me (like cheating)?</p>
<input type="radio" name="q3"> Yes<br>
<input type="radio" name="q3"> I would never cheat<br>
<input type="radio" name="q3"> I'm loyal<br>

<p>Will you reply even when you are asleep?</p>
<input type="radio" name="q4"> Yes<br>
<input type="radio" name="q4"> Yeah<br>
<input type="radio" name="q4"> Yep<br>

<p>Do you promise not to disappear during arguments?</p>
<input type="radio" name="q5"> I promise<br>
<input type="radio" name="q5"> I swear<br>
<input type="radio" name="q5"> Of course, why not baby<br>

<p>Do you promise to always come back to me?</p>
<input type="radio" name="q6"> Yes<br>
<input type="radio" name="q6"> Always<br>
<input type="radio" name="q6"> I promise<br>

<hr>

<h3>💗 PERSONAL QUESTIONS 💗</h3>

<p>Do you see me as your future wife?</p>
<input type="radio" name="p1"> Yes<br>
<input type="radio" name="p1"> No<br>

<p>Do you truly love me?</p>
<input type="radio" name="p2"> Yes<br>
<input type="radio" name="p2"> No<br>

<p>Will you stay through highs and lows?</p>
<input type="radio" name="p3"> Yes<br>
<input type="radio" name="p3"> No<br>

<p>Do you trust me? Be honest.</p>
<input type="radio" name="p4"> Yes<br>
<input type="radio" name="p4"> No<br>

<p>Am I annoying?</p>
<input type="radio" name="p5"> Yes<br>
<input type="radio" name="p5"> No<br>

<p>Will you be my husband?</p>
<input type="radio" name="p6"> Yes<br>
<input type="radio" name="p6"> No<br>

<hr>

<h3>📝 ESSAY SECTION 📝</h3>

<p>Will you choose me over your greatest love?</p>
<textarea rows="2" style="width:100%"></textarea>

<p>How about your mom? (be honest)</p>
<textarea rows="2" style="width:100%"></textarea>

<p>Will you stay even if I’m too much or hard to handle?</p>
<textarea rows="2" style="width:100%"></textarea>

<p>Will you still love me if I was a worm?</p>
<textarea rows="2" style="width:100%"></textarea>

<p>A dinosaur? ror</p>
<textarea rows="2" style="width:100%"></textarea>

<p>Describe me:</p>
<textarea rows="2" style="width:100%"></textarea>

<p>What do you love about me?</p>
<textarea rows="2" style="width:100%"></textarea>

<hr>

<h3>⚠️ CONSEQUENCE SECTION ⚠️</h3>

<p>If you break this contract, choose a consequence:</p>
<input type="radio" name="c1"> Cut off your "dih"<br>
<input type="radio" name="c1"> Cut it<br>
<input type="radio" name="c1"> Cutting the dih<br>

<p>Penalty for making me sulk:</p>
<input type="radio" name="c2"> Send me a message<br>
<input type="radio" name="c2"> Call and apologize<br>
<input type="radio" name="c2"> Give me extra attention<br>

<button onclick="show()">Submit Contract</button>

<div class="result" id="result">
🎉 Now that it’s settled, we are officially unofficially married 💖😂
</div>

</div>

<script>
function show(){
  document.getElementById("result").style.display="block";
}
</script>

</body>
                                          </html>
